text: The Fiat Palio is a car produced by Fiat. It has been produced in various countries. It replaced the Fiat Duna in 1996. == Engines == * 1.2 8V 44 kW (60 hp) and 54 kW (73 hp) * 1.2 16V 59 kW (80 hp) * 1.6 16V 74 kW (101 hp) and 76 kW (103 hp) * 1.7 TD 51 kW (69 hp) * 1.9 D 46 kW (63 hp) * 1.9 JTD 59 kW (80 hp) ==Other websites== * Palio Category:Front wheel drive vehicles Category:1990s automobiles Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles
